question: Display stunt coordinators and fight scene coordinators with ten years of experience.
sql_query1:
SELECT Stunts.Coordinator as name
FROM Stunts
WHERE Stunts.Experience = "10 years"
UNION
SELECT FightScenes.Choreographer as name
FROM FightScenes
WHERE FightScenes.Experience = "10 years"
sql_query2:

interpretation1: Which stunt and fight scene coordinators have ten years of experience?
interpretation2: List all stunt coordinators and also display fight scene coordinators with ten years of experience.
